{"tid":1981802,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"葵涌差館汽油彈案 警長涉自導自演被捕","createTime":"2020-04-21T01:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T05:47:05.000Z","uid":23833,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"967521cc6ff76506869a77c0eda3e024e4f73a0d","tid":1981802,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:11:43.000Z","msg":"本報訊】葵青警區一名警長涉嫌策劃本月中葵涌警署外一宗汽油彈案，警方拘捕放置者，追查後懷疑有人透過中間人再自編自導案件，意圖造成社會輿論，嫁禍抗爭者，之後佯裝調查再破案。警方新界北總區重案組經深入追查，昨日在秀茂坪以涉嫌妨礙司法公正罪名將警長拘捕。消息稱，有人被捕後否認涉案，聲稱被誣衊，警方仍在調查涉案警長犯案動機，不排除有更多人被捕。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200421/UG7KUV7WRORAP44AHCVNSLBU34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200421%2FUG7KUV7WRORAP44AHCVNSLBU34%2F&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0Kzf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=72404afb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200421%2FUG7KUV7WRORAP44AHCVNSLBU34%2F&h=bcbb1c28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200421/UG7KUV7WRORAP44AHCVNSLBU34/</a>"},{"pid":"297952b40c5d310d463e885a413625f6c3726003","tid":1981802,"uid":207977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />3萬thx"},{"pid":"df408749bc9d713327bca6166702a73a5536bfe9","tid":1981802,"uid":59447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:14:17.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c0a720e3c840581c1dcb1e582c11a86a7f8ffd","tid":1981802,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T01:16:09.000Z","msg":"小強：已訓斥"},{"pid":"10cce45a31588cba102e0ee1fe4946902fe5baf5","tid":1981802,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T02:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p